Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,原來真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你在猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你想放逐到地獄的真的是那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不 肯定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,秋野對著我笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,還有其他人也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一起聊天的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,井本 遠藤 緒方 神谷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,每人只能將一個人流放到地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,別太貪心了 大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎 不能想想辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,走了 菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜一下再來吧 大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 這麼晚了還大吼大叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才說「救救我」了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,都說沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,別管我
