Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,發起這個話題的人是eve
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:36.95,zhu,,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰啊
